4. API Documentation (API Documentation)

4.1. Endpoint: /register

Method: POST

Description: Registers a new user.

Parameters:

Password (line): User's password.

Answer:

200 OK: Password hash in JSON format:

{

"Hashed_password": "$2b$12$Mo3LQ.Cs7h20y/KP1EoUTub6vyAQ3Dh.Qa5/07.9gAt6dIrCirj/W"

}

4.2. Endpoint: /login

Method: POST

Description: Authorises the user, returns the JWT token.

Parameters:

Password (line): User's password.

Totp (line): TOTP code.

Answer:

200 OK: Successful login and JWT token:

{

"Message": "Login successful",

"Token": "<JWT_TOKEN>"

}

4.3. Endpoint: /password_reset_request

Method: POST

Description: Requests password reset, sends email with token.

Parameters:

Email (line): User's email.

Answer:

200 OK: Message that email has been sent:

{

"Message": "Password reset email sent"

}

4.4. Endpoint: /reset_password/<token>

Method: POST

Description: Resets the user password by token.

Parameters:

Password (line): New user password.

Answer:

200 OK: Message about successful password reset:

{

"Message": "Password successfully reset"

}